videos.description: Tennessee's Jordan Bone hops through the lane for the easy basket.
videos.headline: Bone drives through traffic for the smooth layup

videos.description: Auburn's Chuma Okeke steals it away and throws one down on the fast break on the other end.
videos.headline: Okeke rips one away for a slam

videos.description: Auburn's Samir Doughty pads the Tigers' lead over Tennessee late in the second half with a clutch 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Doughty's drains big 3-pointer for Auburn

videos.description: After upsetting No. 5 Tennessee, Auburn's players share the moment with the home crowd.
